description: Returns a list of resource metadata for a given list of development endpoint names. After calling the ListDevEndpoints operation, you can call this operation to access the data to which you have been granted permissions. This operation supports all IAM permissions, including permission conditions that uses tags.

nested_items.name: DevEndpoints
nested_items.description: A list of DevEndpoint definitions.

nested_items.name: EndpointName
nested_items.description: The name of the DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: RoleArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role used in this DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: SecurityGroupIds
nested_items.description: A list of security group identifiers used in this DevEndpoint.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: SubnetId
nested_items.description: The subnet ID for this DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: YarnEndpointAddress
nested_items.description: The YARN endpoint address used by this DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: PrivateAddress
nested_items.description: A private IP address to access the DevEndpoint within a VPC if the DevEndpoint is created within one. The PrivateAddress field is present only when you create the DevEndpoint within your VPC.

nested_items.name: ZeppelinRemoteSparkInterpreterPort
nested_items.description: The Apache Zeppelin port for the remote Apache Spark interpreter.

nested_items.name: PublicAddress
nested_items.description: The public IP address used by this DevEndpoint. The PublicAddress field is present only when you create a non-virtual private cloud (VPC) DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The current status of this DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: WorkerType
nested_items.description: The type of predefined worker that is allocated to the development endpoint. Accepts a value of Standard, G.1X, or G.2X.
For the Standard worker type, each worker provides 4 vCPU, 16 GB of memory and a 50GB disk, and 2 executors per worker.

nested_items.type: 4 vCPU, 16 GB of memory, 64 GB disk
nested_items.description: For the G.1X worker type, each worker maps to 1 DPU (4 vCPU, 16 GB of memory, 64 GB disk), and provides 1 executor per worker. We recommend this worker type for memory-intensive jobs.

nested_items.type: 8 vCPU, 32 GB of memory, 128 GB disk
nested_items.description: For the G.2X worker type, each worker maps to 2 DPU (8 vCPU, 32 GB of memory, 128 GB disk), and provides 1 executor per worker. We recommend this worker type for memory-intensive jobs.

nested_items.name: GlueVersion
nested_items.description: Glue version determines the versions of Apache Spark and Python that Glue supports. The Python version indicates the version supported for running your ETL scripts on development endpoints.

nested_items.name: NumberOfWorkers
nested_items.description: The number of workers of a defined workerType that are allocated to the development endpoint.

nested_items.name: NumberOfNodes
nested_items.description: The number of Glue Data Processing Units (DPUs) allocated to this DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: AvailabilityZone
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services Availability Zone where this DevEndpoint is located.

nested_items.name: VpcId
nested_items.description: The ID of the virtual private cloud (VPC) used by this DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: ExtraPythonLibsS3Path
nested_items.description: The paths to one or more Python libraries in an Amazon S3 bucket that should be loaded in your DevEndpoint. Multiple values must be complete paths separated by a comma.

nested_items.name: ExtraJarsS3Path
nested_items.description: The path to one or more Java .jar files in an S3 bucket that should be loaded in your DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: FailureReason
nested_items.description: The reason for a current failure in this DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: LastUpdateStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the last update.

nested_items.name: CreatedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The point in time at which this DevEndpoint was created.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedTimestamp
nested_items.description: The point in time at which this DevEndpoint was last modified.

nested_items.name: PublicKey
nested_items.description: The public key to be used by this DevEndpoint for authentication. This attribute is provided for backward compatibility because the recommended attribute to use is public keys.

nested_items.name: PublicKeys
nested_items.description: A list of public keys to be used by the DevEndpoints for authentication. Using this attribute is preferred over a single public key because the public keys allow you to have a different private key per client.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: SecurityConfiguration
nested_items.description: The name of the SecurityConfiguration structure to be used with this DevEndpoint.

nested_items.name: Arguments
nested_items.description: A map of arguments used to configure the DevEndpoint.
"--enable-glue-datacatalog": ""

nested_items.name: DevEndpointsNotFound
nested_items.description: A list of DevEndpoints not found.
(string) ---
